description: AI art prompt to design a bold, modern sports poster of a Pakistan cricket player celebrating a century in the Asia Cup. Features a large dramatic profile portrait in the background with dynamic green and white abstract strokes, and a full-body foreground figure raising his bat high in triumph. Perfect for generating high-energy, patriotic sports visuals.
AI prompt to create a hyper-realistic portrait of a billiards player. A man in a brown polo jersey leans over a blue pool table, focusing on a shot. Uses detailed clothing and pose description.

This prompt creates a Renaissance painting style high-speed motion blur photo of a soccer player mid-kick. Features dramatic dark background, moody spotlighting, glowing teal (#02B2CA) and violet (#AC03FC) motion trails, realistic athletic pose, and cinematic sports photography aesthetic.
